name: @hapi/hoek
readme: # hoek Utility methods for the hapi ecosystem. This module is not intended to solve every problem for everyone, but rather as a central place to store hapi-specific methods. If you're looking for a general purpose utility module, check out [lodash](https://github.com/lodash/lodash) or [underscore](https://github.com/jashkenas/underscore). [![Build Status](https://secure.travis-ci.org/hapijs/hoek.svg)](http://travis-ci.org/hapijs/hoek) ## Documentation [**API Reference**](API.md)
